{"tid":1606344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【10.1唔係END GAME】明天目標仍然係不被捕！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-30T14:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T08:59:43.000Z","uid":162866,"like":49,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8d172ac8dc3f61df743cff618c27a9d4f753956c","tid":1606344,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"好多人又係到渲染最後一戰氣氛<br />\n<br />\n但大家唔好比氣氛衝昏頭腦<br />\n<br />\n要冷靜，有咩做到既就做，做唔到既唔好格硬來送頭，比狗拉左就等於少個人企出來<br />\n<br />\n中共內衰已經浮現緊出來<br />\n<br />\n中國威脅論都已經係全球spread緊<br />\n<br />\n中共唔會長命得過我地<br />\n<br />\n無必要一時意氣用事令到自己輸<br />\n<br />\n勇武有咩危險見唔對路就即走<br />\n<br />\n唔洗話掩護和理非走先<br />\n<br />\n和理為盾唔係得個講字<br />\n<br />\n無裝和理非都唔洗怕比人拉<br />\n<br />\n你乜柒都無佢最多塔你48小時曠工一日<br />\n<br />\n總之大家聽日萬事小心"},{"pid":"49365082eea093b4b32964c3dd0b65d2ad76cd0a","tid":1606344,"uid":5373,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:12:17.000Z","msg":"被捕=End game <br />\n不被捕 為首要"},{"pid":"3800eedf79a6fae732f3cb76a67148bce5839c90","tid":1606344,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">賀佢老母</span>"},{"pid":"ff6fb061fd5486bc3ac23b392f086e8bcb55b438","tid":1606344,"uid":150267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"目標：落面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三點燒黨旗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［主線］<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日一定要做啲有標誌性嘅</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604870</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武 和理非入<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"> 依到有合集帶啲咩</span></strong><br />\n［整合］<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一執齊野</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603888</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">